snippet.title: Devs Play: Gas Station Simulator
snippet.description:
Watch Mercus, one of the programmers on the project, play the demo of Gas Stations Simulator and giving some insights into the game.
Get the demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149620/Gas_Station_Simulator/
